This is a state charity event that we have been planning for two years.
We decided to take advantage of the marketing potential of the end of the Mayan calendar set for December 21 at 11:10 in the morning.
The day before, on 20 December at 9 p.m., we will organize 3 simultaneous concerts in Prague, Brno and Ostrava.
